Champion a Woman She will build a nation is the tag line. ChampionWoman strives to impact women and girls to becone carrer intentional and be financially independent. This is done by conducting Chmapionwoman training on life leadership for women and girls. The popular broad topics are Self Esteem building, Managing relationships, Stress Management, work life integration, parenting etc. The vision is to create a generation of calm, resilient and powerful women.
